{"id":270780,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/维权网-上海异议人士谢丹因组织同城公民聚会被/","date":"2012-12-27T09:15:49Z","modified":"2012-12-27T09:15:49Z","title":"维权网 | 上海异议人士谢丹因组织同城公民聚会被封QQ","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员钟剑报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>，上海异议人士谢丹（网名佐罗）发现自己的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">QQ</span><span>号（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">286692568</span><span>）被封。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>继上月上海公民成功举办会餐，吸引约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span><span>人参加之后，本月，谢丹等一批上海公民再次筹划同城聚餐。他们选择的地点还是甲私房菜馆，时间是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4-8</span><span>点钟，地址是上海市徐汇区番禺路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1207</span><span>号。谢丹在多个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">QQ</span><span>群里发布了上海公民聚餐的信息，并且提供了详细的坐车方法以及地图。会餐实行</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">AA</span><span>制，每人约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span><span>元。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上月上海公民举行聚餐之前，国保就进行了多方阻挠，上海民运人士高晓亮、异议人士李化平等人都被国保以喝茶或喝咖啡的方式限制了人身自由。而谢丹的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">QQ</span><span>号被封，是本次上海公民组织会餐以来遇到的第一个阻遏行动。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>联系电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">021-6448-1078</span></div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}